EQUIX CLUB

All the data you give us when you apply will be treated with absolute confidentiality and will not be available to anyone on the web. Members cannot communicate via the web or create any profiles.


Unlike other clubs and websites, we organize events but we are not a dating website, which guarantees the maximum privacy of all the people who come to our events and private parties.


To attend any EQUIX event you must first apply as a guest or member.


If you are accepted, we will respond with the payment method to pay the corresponding fee.


Couples who cannot afford to be members but wish to enjoy some events as guests can join by paying a one off fee.

They will be able to access each event at a basic price and the approved guest category entitles them to participate in contests.


Single ladies are welcome under the same category as approved guests.


Single gentlemen are invited to join the club if they wish, although some events are reserved for couples and single ladies only.


Some events are themed and require a dress code that must be met.

For all other events all gentlemen are required to wear a proper tuxedo with bow tie.

Ladies shall be elegantly dressed in evening wear or lingerie covered with a coat.



FEES:


Approved Guests: one off joining fee.

Couples and single gentlemen: £300

Single ladies: £100

Red circle: £9000 per annum.

It is the entry level of Equix membership and the minimum requirement for every single gentleman to attend any event.

Special events and rooms for members.


Golden circle: £150,000 joining fee. Thereafter, renewal payments are due on March 5th 2025.


VIP Tables, private events and exclusive matchmaking services.


Diamond Membership:

By invitation only for Golden members after a minimum of attended events.

A very limited number of places are available. Special events and benefits.




Events are announced on our bio pages LNK.BIO/EQUIX & LINKTR.EE/EQUIX_CLUB
